You find yourself lying on a huge pillow, one so gigantic that it covers the
entire floor!  The walls are lined with blue and violet down comforters.
Even though this room looks like it might pass for a fluffy rubber room, it's
strangely relaxing in here.  The most spectacular part of the hideaway is the
ceiling made out of a magnifying glass.  The glass displays the stars so
vividly that you feel like you could almost reach out a touch one...
